        <Parent_String>tables by location or context: rooms or spaces [300165793], tables by location or context [300165791], tables (support furniture) [300039548], support furniture [300039337], furniture by form or function [300048628], furniture [300037680], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
